    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"tableOfContents":"","html":"<p>때는 2010년대 <code class=\"language-jstext\">Bootstrap 3</code>이 풍미하고 있던 시절,<br>\n부가 유료 theme없이 네이티브만으로도 멋지던 그 때.</p>\n<p>아직 그 디자인을 사용하는 프로젝트가 있다면 어떨까?<br>\n<em>믿기지 않겠지만 많다.</em></p>\n<ol>\n<li>레거시 사랑<br>\n아직 누가 3을 쓰고 있을까..?<br>\n심지어 새로운 프로젝트에도 쓴다하면 어떨까?<br>\n과거의 영광이 프로젝트화된다면 이걸까?</li>\n<li>버전업 문제<br>\n이미 통째로 이식했기에 연관된 스크립트가 쌔고 쌨다 (aka 불가능)<br>\n뒷목의 안부를 묻게된다</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/\">Bootstrap</a>은 현재 5.1.1버전을 서비스한다<br>\n<a href=\"https://keenthemes.com/metronic/\">metronic</a>이라는 theme을 함께 사용하는데 현재 5 기준 서비스되고 있다</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/8b70b/metronic8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"metronic default dashboard demo1\"\n        title=\"metronic default dashboard demo1\"\n        src=\"/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/0a47e/metronic8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/8a4e8/metronic8.png 150w,\n/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/5a46d/metronic8.png 300w,\n/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/0a47e/metronic8.png 600w,\n/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/1cfc2/metronic8.png 900w,\n/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/c1b63/metronic8.png 1200w,\n/static/5c20dc733804878b41557feb5c6ed733/8b70b/metronic8.png 1266w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<em><a href=\"https://preview.keenthemes.com/metronic8/demo1/index.html?_ga=2.170569824.1519457692.1631668186-192319790.1631668186\">metronic8 default dashboard demo1</a>의 캡쳐본</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/5c98f/metronic4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"metronic dashboard admin1\"\n        title=\"metronic dashboard admin1\"\n        src=\"/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/0a47e/metronic4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/8a4e8/metronic4.png 150w,\n/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/5a46d/metronic4.png 300w,\n/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/0a47e/metronic4.png 600w,\n/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/1cfc2/metronic4.png 900w,\n/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/c1b63/metronic4.png 1200w,\n/static/61c7e2a5efa4788a2e58a2a45e8b1faf/5c98f/metronic4.png 1283w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<em><a href=\"https://preview.keenthemes.com/metronic-v4/theme/admin_1/\">metronic4 admin1</a>의 캡쳐본</em><br>\n3버전 샘플은 도저히 찾을 수가 없다😢</p>\n<p>예